     1	"""Phrase capture writer — persists qualifying phrases to ``samples/<source>/``.
     2	
     3	Wraps :class:`PhraseTracker` with a buffer that accumulates input while a
     4	play session is in progress and flushes to a timestamped file once
     5	``phrase_ended`` fires. Sub-threshold bursts are dropped without I/O.
     6	
     7	Two sources are supported:
     8	
     9	* ``"keyboard"`` — buffer entries are ``(rel_seconds, midi_bytes)`` tuples
    10	  and are persisted as a Standard MIDI File (Type 0).
    11	* ``"theramini"`` — buffer entries are float sample arrays and are
    12	  persisted as 16-bit PCM mono WAV.
    13	
    14	Each captured sample is paired with a sidecar ``.json`` metadata file
    15	containing instrument/song_id/key/tempo/timestamp/duration/source tags.
